It seems impossible to close my account at experfy.com

I have traversed the menu, google searched etc, but couldn't find a way to delist and/or remove my account from their website.

Support didn't answer my ticket.

Instead, I have resorted to writing a bunch of foul words in my account in an attempt to get banned.
